<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Starfield Mechanic</title>
    <!-- STYLES -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/shared.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/landing-page.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="background"></div>
    <header>
      <h3>Do you have what it takes to be a</h3>
      <h1>STARFIELD MECHANIC?</h1>
      <h2>A Strategy Game</h2>
      <img
        id="title-image"
        src="/images/title.png"
        alt="5 mechanics posing and with various tools at the ready"
      />
      <p>
        The year is 3500. The galaxy is bustling with hundreds of life-bearing
        planets, each with countless factories, ships, satellites, and other
        machines! And when things go down, there’s only one place to call:
        Starfield Mechanics, the best traveling mechanic service in the known
        galaxy!
      </p>
      <p>
        You’re fresh out of your apprenticeship and itching to earn those sweet
        intersystem quills! After all, that retirement cabin on Mars won’t pay
        for itself. So grab your toolbox, lace up your safety-toe shoes, and
        fire up your spaceship! It’s time to fix some machines!
      </p>
    </header>
    <main>
      <!-- %- include('includes/landing-page/waiting-room') %> -->
      <div class="this-or-that">
        <form id="start-new-game" action="/" method="POST">
          <button type="submit" id="new-game-button">Start a New Game</button>
        </form>
      </div>
      <div><h3>OR</h3></div>
      <div class="this-or-that">
        <form id="join-room" method="get">
          <label for="room-input">Enter a Room Code</label>
          <div>
            <input type="text" id="room-input" />
            <button type="submit" id="join-room-button">Join</button>
          </div>
        </form>
      </div>
    </main>
    <!-- SCRIPTS -->
    <script src="/socket.io/socket.io.js"></script>
    <script src="/scripts/landing-page.js"></script>
    <!-- <script src="/scripts/waiting-room.js"></script> -->
  </body>
</html>
